// Testimonials Component
---

<section class="testimonials" id="testimonials">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="testimonials-header text-center">
      <h2>What Our Customers Say</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Join thousands of satisfied customers who trust Nature's Essence</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="testimonials-grid">
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">"I've been using Nature's Essence products for over a year now, and the quality is unmatched. Their essential oils are pure and potent, and I love knowing they're sustainably sourced. Highly recommend!"</p>
