          <img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=13" alt="Michael Chen" />
          <div class="author-info">
            <h4>Michael Chen</h4>
            <p>Professional Chef</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">"As someone with sensitive skin, finding natural beauty products that actually work has been a challenge. Nature's Essence exceeded my expectations. My skin has never looked better!"</p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=5" alt="Emily Rodriguez" />
          <div class="author-info">
            <h4>Emily Rodriguez</h4>
            <p>Beauty Blogger</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">"Outstanding customer service and exceptional products. I've recommended Nature's Essence to all my friends and family. Their aromatherapy oils have become an essential part of my daily routine."</p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=33" alt="David Thompson" />
          <div class="author-info">
            <h4>David Thompson</h4>
            <p>Yoga Instructor</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">"The quality and purity of their products are evident from the first use. I love that they're transparent about their sourcing and committed to sustainability. A brand I can trust completely."</p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=9" alt="Lisa Anderson" />
          <div class="author-info">
            <h4>Lisa Anderson</h4>
            <p>Holistic Practitioner</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">"From their packaging to their products, everything screams quality and care for the environment. Nature's Essence has become my go-to for all things natural and wellness-related."</p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=14" alt="James Wilson" />
          <div class="author-info">
            <h4>James Wilson</h4>
            <p>Environmental Advocate</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials {
    background: var(--color-white);
  }
  
  .testimonials-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }
  
  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .testimonials-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
  }
  
  .testimonial-card {
    background: var(--color-background);
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
    transition: all var(--transition-normal);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  
  .testimonial-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    border-left-color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  
  .stars {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }
  
  .testimonial-text {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    flex-grow: 1;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  
  .testimonial-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: auto;
  }
  
  .testimonial-author img {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
  }
  
  .author-info h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  
  .author-info p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .testimonials-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
